creator: HostelYab
descriptionHtml:
Find the right subtitles for all of your movies and shows as soon as possible. A simple design, autocomplete search suggestions and easy download let you just start watching.


- By default, subtitles are stored in the GetSub folder.

- In the program settings, you can change the language and location of the subtitles.

- All subtitles files are in srt format. You can use programs such as MX Player or VLC Player to play your videos with subtitles.
